{"tid":1342722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"時代革命時機將至，號召和理非焦土第一擊","createTime":"2019-07-21T17:53:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T18:28:23.000Z","uid":268559,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a3284913026d0c7aba2386d76b1812054709fc0f","tid":1342722,"uid":268559,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T17:53:25.000Z","msg":"不合作運動（英語：Non-cooperation movement），又稱非暴力不合作運動，是世界歷史上第一個全國性的非暴力反抗運動，由律師出身的印度國民大會黨領袖聖雄甘地。他發動和領導了1920&mdash;1922年和1930&mdash;1934年全國範圍的非暴力不合作運動。 第一次世界大戰結束後（1918年），英國對印度的統治轉趨嚴厲，反英運動隨之興起，要求獨立自治的呼聲高張。甘地呼籲以非暴力的不合作手段，抵制英國的統治。他要求印度人<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">不納稅</span></span>。。。不購買英貨。 (來源: 維基百科) <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">立即開始大量文宣工作<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">抗稅運動，香港人唔好再出錢俾黑犬烚番自已</span></span></span></span>"},{"pid":"d95dd840f877dc1d0bdac35ea5bb171749684bc8","tid":1342722,"uid":268559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:15:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8df2d2278a8c91068f14b63eb8ec52941f07fbc2","tid":1342722,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:17:32.000Z","msg":"唔納稅可以直接係銀行扣<br />\n搵方法令政府行政費高於稅額比較可行"},{"pid":"ab1dcfb135d13ac1f06b5d798bfda31771b09cc6","tid":1342722,"uid":89184,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:17:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有乘客在港鐵內受傷應可賠償? </span></strong>"},{"pid":"5dac197edd23afb85004bba009548081573d64e1","tid":1342722,"uid":109433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T18:18:34.000Z","msg":"仲要交稅養埋死廢警<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"892d468f1b13fa0abc198c31b405b3aa37e21d10","tid":1342722,"uid":268559,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ab1dcfb135d13ac1f06b5d798bfda31771b09cc6","tid":1342722,"uid":89184,"like":